Package etomica.virial

Class ClusterWheatleySoftDerivatives

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.virial.ClusterWheatleySoftDerivatives
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClusterAbstract, ClusterAbstractMultivalue
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClusterWheatleyMultibodyDerivatives

    public class ClusterWheatleySoftDerivatives
extends java.lang.Object
implements ClusterAbstract, ClusterAbstractMultivalue
    This class calculates the sum of all biconnected clusters using Wheatley's recursive formulation.

      • setBDAccFrac

        public void setBDAccFrac​(double p,
                         IRandom rng)
        Directs this cluster to only compute p fraction of the time when the value is too small (below tol). When it is computed, the value will be boosted by 1/p.
        Parameters:
        p - the fraction of time BD values will be computed
        rng - the random number generated used to decide to do BD or not
